{"thi-ap9:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap9:0.2":"Sumedhavagga ","thi-ap9:0.3":"Pancadipikatheriapadana ","thi-ap9:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","thi-ap9:1.2":"cariki asaham tada; ","thi-ap9:1.3":"Aramena ca aramam, ","thi-ap9:1.4":"carami kusalatthika. ","thi-ap9:2.1":"Kalapakkhamhi divase, ","thi-ap9:2.2":"addasam bodhimuttamam; ","thi-ap9:2.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","thi-ap9:2.4":"bodhimule nisidaham. ","thi-ap9:3.1":"Garucittam upatthetva, ","thi-ap9:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","thi-ap9:3.3":"Somanassam pavedetva, ","thi-ap9:3.4":"evam cintesi tavade. ","thi-ap9:4.1":"‘Yadi buddho amitaguno, ","thi-ap9:4.2":"asamappatipuggalo; ","thi-ap9:4.3":"Dassetu patihiram me, ","thi-ap9:4.4":"bodhi obhasatu ayam’. ","thi-ap9:5.1":"Saha avajjite mayham, ","thi-ap9:5.2":"bodhi pajjali tavade; ","thi-ap9:5.3":"Sabbasonnamaya asi, ","thi-ap9:5.4":"disa sabba virocati. ","thi-ap9:6.1":"Sattarattindivam tattha, ","thi-ap9:6.2":"bodhimule nisidaham; ","thi-ap9:6.3":"Sattame divase patte, ","thi-ap9:6.4":"dipapujam akasaham. ","thi-ap9:7.1":"Asanam parivaretva, ","thi-ap9:7.2":"panca dipani pajjalum; ","thi-ap9:7.3":"Yava udeti suriyo, ","thi-ap9:7.4":"dipa me pajjalum tada. ","thi-ap9:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap9:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap9:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap9:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap9:9.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","thi-ap9:9.2":"pancadipati vuccati; ","thi-ap9:9.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","thi-ap9:9.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","thi-ap9:10.1":"Asankhiyani dipani, ","thi-ap9:10.2":"parivare jalanti me; ","thi-ap9:10.3":"Yavata devabhavanam, ","thi-ap9:10.4":"dipalokena jotati. ","thi-ap9:11.1":"Parammukha nisiditva, ","thi-ap9:11.2":"yadi icchami passitum; ","thi-ap9:11.3":"Uddham adho ca tiriyam, ","thi-ap9:11.4":"sabbam passami cakkhuna. ","thi-ap9:12.1":"Yavata abhikankhami, ","thi-ap9:12.2":"datthum sugataduggate; ","thi-ap9:12.3":"Tattha avaranam natthi, ","thi-ap9:12.4":"rukkhesu pabbatesu va. ","thi-ap9:13.1":"Asiti devarajunam, ","thi-ap9:13.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap9:13.3":"Satanam cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap9:13.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap9:14.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","thi-ap9:14.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","thi-ap9:14.3":"Dipasatasahassani, ","thi-ap9:14.4":"parivare jalanti me. ","thi-ap9:15.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","thi-ap9:15.2":"uppajjim matukucchiyam; ","thi-ap9:15.3":"Matukucchigata santi, ","thi-ap9:15.4":"akkhi me na nimilati. ","thi-ap9:16.1":"Dipasatasahassani, ","thi-ap9:16.2":"punnakammasamangita; ","thi-ap9:16.3":"Jalanti sutikagehe, ","thi-ap9:16.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap9:17.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap9:17.2":"manasam vinivattayim; ","thi-ap9:17.3":"Ajaramatam sitibhavam, ","thi-ap9:17.4":"nibbanam phassayim aham. ","thi-ap9:18.1":"Jatiya sattavassaham, ","thi-ap9:18.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","thi-ap9:18.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","thi-ap9:18.4":"gunamannaya gotamo. ","thi-ap9:19.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","thi-ap9:19.2":"pasadesu guhasu va; ","thi-ap9:19.3":"Sunnagare vasantiya, ","thi-ap9:19.4":"pancadipa jalanti me. ","thi-ap9:20.1":"Dibbacakkhuvisuddham me, ","thi-ap9:20.2":"samadhikusala aham; ","thi-ap9:20.3":"Abhinnaparamippatta, ","thi-ap9:20.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap9:21.1":"Sabbavositavosana, ","thi-ap9:21.2":"katakicca anasava; ","thi-ap9:21.3":"Pancadipa mahavira, ","thi-ap9:21.4":"pade vandami cakkhuma. ","thi-ap9:22.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap9:22.2":"yam dipamadadim tada; ","thi-ap9:22.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap9:22.4":"pancadipanidam phalam. ","thi-ap9:23.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap9:23.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap9:23.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap9:24.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap9:24.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap9:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap9:25.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap9:25.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap9:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap9:26.1":"Ittham sudam pancadipika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap9:27.1":"Pancadipikatheriyapadanam navamam. "}